Usage: mwdev [<stuff>]

--clone --<type> <name>               Clones the extension or skin into the correct directory
--extension-report                    Stuff to help you manage extensions
--missing-extensions                  Lists missing extensions and optionally clones them with --clone
--missing-skins                       Lists missing skins and optionally clones them with --clone
--msg-hook                            Adds the Gerrit commit-msg hook to the git repo you are in
--update-composer                     Updates a requirement in a composer.json file for a given skin or extension
--help                                Provides help. (Can be used with commands listed above)
